Package nl.utwente.jmlplugin.completion

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JMLAssignableClauseCompletionProvider
    Provides completion suggestions when invoked in assignable clauses.
    JMLCompletionConfidence
    This class tells IntelliJ to always pop-up the completion suggestions.
    JMLCompletionContributor
    Class that provides non-referential completion support.
    JMLCompletionUtils
    Various utility methods that are needed by the various completion providers.
    JMLJavaBackslashCompletionProvider
    Provides completion for \jmlkeywords in Java+JML expressions.
    JMLJavaDotCompletionProvider
    Provides completions for "." java expressions.
    JMLJavaExceptionClassProvider
    Provides completions for all visible exception classes in the project (all exceptions that subclass Throwable)
    JMLJavaIdentifierCompletionProvider
    Class that is responsible for adding completion contributions for when a completion is called on a lone Java identifier, it resolves static imports, class methods, class field references and adds them to the completion set.
    JMLJavaPrimitiveClassCompletion  
    JMLKeywordCompletionProvider
    Class that provides the list of completable JML keywords.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JMLCompletionUtils.expressionLocation
    Enum for JML expression location, this is needed for context aware completion of JML keywords that can be mixed with Java.
    JMLCompletionWeights
    Enum for providing completion priority weights by which to order completion suggestions when they are displayed.
